{"tid":1834314,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全港區議員出黎，正面要求政府封關，幫手推","createTime":"2020-01-22T10:30:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-23T04:06:27.000Z","uid":216683,"like":88,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"2f9d481c0ed242ea5fec4cb79a4f2e55dbcd5abb","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:30:02.000Z","msg":"政府唔封，姐係搵市民條命黎玩，賭唔會有事<br />\n姐係唔會做任何野防禦<br />\n<br />\n出於私心，俾班所謂中立派都一齊反政府<br />\n有可能d怕死藍絲都轉過黎呢邊<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，大家係連登開幾多post都無用<br />\n不如集合哂所有議員<br />\n黎個大行動<br />\n<br />\n星期五晚集體請求又好<br />\n星期五大罷工，叫政府封關又好<br />\n<br />\n好過大家等到新年放假，等出事<br />\n<br />\n大家要做嘅野好簡單<br />\n就係封返自己區嘅區議員<br />\n叫佢地一齊聯合做野<br />\n<br />\n唔叫佢地未必會郁<br />\n<br />\n只有大家齊心，一齊叫<br />\n先會叫得郁班區議員"},{"pid":"730cbdfb3d14b59936d39534966cafcce1fc6df1","tid":1834314,"uid":83910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:30:51.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ceb854ee0004bd2d04190897db0f21e19a1f1c04","tid":1834314,"uid":287211,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:32:31.000Z","msg":"封了 吊 之前無高鐵 生活又咁過<br />\n點解唔肯封"},{"pid":"b18acd2c40edec6843075b8e268b68414d6c58f9","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:37:00.000Z","msg":"幫手去自己區個區議員到留言：<br />\n<br />\n請支持全港第二個，全港區議員召集行動<br />\n集合全港意見、民選議員，要求政府封關做好防禦<br />\n<br />\n1. 病毒傳到落香港，你唔想經濟差香港都會經濟差<br />\n2. 政府聲稱準備好床位應付大型感染，倒不如唔好俾人感染，封關保平安<br />\n3. 政府高官遲遲唔做實事，提升嚴重級別但實際無做好關口檢疫工作，引至帶病毒者走入市區，傳播病毒<br />\n<br />\n區議員立即互相聯絡<br />\n新年前作出行動<br />\n<br />\n否則新年人潮後病毒一定大型擴散"},{"pid":"a59543813b9692a604533dbf2507334535b94e2a","tid":1834314,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:38:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cbfa0daa18baa06d9bb8ace1e434e71e02a7994","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"係連登開n個post都唔會推到有人做野<br />\n大家快d推區議員一齊做野啦"},{"pid":"8ba2baf151f1de23defa33a47c3722f8c110954f","tid":1834314,"uid":223643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:40:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9c68fef1442334076befb8793fc034bf35485a","tid":1834314,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e32c1e05d102f31399cf34bf7c879fc5dac1781e","tid":1834314,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:40:25.000Z","msg":"一定要make noise<br />\n第時有咩事可以夾埋黃藍一齊清算"},{"pid":"9bbc45cf094181496529717d91b8bd9639bc3647","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"理大救手足個次都肯集人<br />\n希望今次區議員再次做野"},{"pid":"7ee1a233b867806b280430b2fe9cb291b4754d2f","tid":1834314,"uid":277363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔好奇怪，之前一直想攬炒<br />\n呢個係真攬炒既時間，變疫埠一定炒到佢仆街<br />\n但依嫁又要拒絕中國病狗黎炒香港"},{"pid":"886ac485795b9eddecb8d7a1e1a8f2714419570b","tid":1834314,"uid":61481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9b1fc9b517b3bcc1118a6a54e6b91ed63ad25c1","tid":1834314,"uid":102982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"c33487197720a075dec8586dd8262c7a0a8884ed","tid":1834314,"uid":102982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:44:45.000Z","msg":"第一個一定要封高鐵！！！"},{"pid":"73f311f5f92e12ac6d32f9562b7c1cf409e58b2c","tid":1834314,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:45:32.000Z","msg":"封關呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff04c279a4661618bf0c19a7ed0711af7f899aeb","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7ee1a233b867806b280430b2fe9cb291b4754d2f","tid":1834314,"uid":277363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔好奇怪，之前一直想攬炒<br />\n呢個係真攬炒既時間，變疫埠一定炒到佢仆街<br />\n但依嫁又要拒絕中國病狗黎炒香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:49:49.000Z","msg":"1. 你覺得真係會封到關？可能啦，但封唔到再大爆發，唔知d仲撐政府嘅人點諗呢？<br />\n有無得加大自己人數量，同令大家燒返起團火，靠今次。政府表現愈on9班人先肯繼續個運動<br />\n<br />\n2. 爆得都攬炒硬，但要攬炒期間拎得到最多民意嘅話要點做？就係係呢場抗疫期間有做實事嘅人<br />\n大家唔出聲唔做野，就會無對比，無對比就唔會更有力同人講要反政府<br />\n<br />\n3. 其實區議員肯郁，我相信我地呢邊拎得到嘅資源會多話班死要面嘅藍絲，攬炒係要，但最尾我地黃色死哂有咩用，就係要死哂對家嘅人<br />\n相個區議會d資源會幫到好多手足"},{"pid":"b97dda83ab81320b68af812e71b091b9415c83f4","tid":1834314,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7ee1a233b867806b280430b2fe9cb291b4754d2f","tid":1834314,"uid":277363,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:42:03.000Z","msg":"連登仔好奇怪，之前一直想攬炒<br />\n呢個係真攬炒既時間，變疫埠一定炒到佢仆街<br />\n但依嫁又要拒絕中國病狗黎炒香港"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:50:59.000Z","msg":"你仆街死啦"},{"pid":"658304247637b83a0643448ebeb13f4b6306ff6c","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"區議員幫手做野啦<br />\n理念<br />\n同集人去理大救手足一樣<br />\n<br />\n幫手團結下香港人啦<br />\n由其係呢排<br />\n呢排大家都心灰咗<br />\n燃起大家嘅火啦<br />\n<br />\n星期五晚要求政府直接封關呀！"},{"pid":"d535c18e1242b53641be50c38c0f647ae304c4a3","tid":1834314,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n如果係西九站搞一次勇武集會都還有一線生機"},{"pid":"83732ab8e1d704055e4bb3527aa382ed46587cfb","tid":1834314,"uid":68111,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:54:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">武漢肺炎 香港封關</span>"},{"pid":"c8e7fd8b445d2f0040da637b7cb8f3fb20b7ea02","tid":1834314,"uid":218447,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:55:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"afd3a1fdf87e34f264a159bcb9e145819902c91d","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d535c18e1242b53641be50c38c0f647ae304c4a3","tid":1834314,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:53:46.000Z","msg":"有撚用咩<br />\n<br />\n如果係西九站搞一次勇武集會都還有一線生機"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:55:54.000Z","msg":"講真<br />\n佢地肯開個頭<br />\n到時會無人？<br />\n<br />\n定你覺得<br />\n唔洗佢地出黎<br />\n自然會有好多人去西九？<br />\n少人連衫都換唔到啦<br />\n<br />\n搵人開個頭先啦"},{"pid":"8fc6a772b8c6fe5dbbcae62bce1ac557d47cf31a","tid":1834314,"uid":216683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:57:59.000Z","msg":"連登推POST都唔夠<br />\n記住要去自己區個區議員到留言呀"},{"pid":"d846a2cbf5669a30c23d25f12a9bd606a947ff97","tid":1834314,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:58:30.000Z","msg":"就算民建聯自己死人<br />\n佢都會自由放中囯人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有&ldquo;&ldquo;新春回鄉&ldquo;&ldquo;返香港果班賤人"},{"pid":"fb88bc4ca04479d9631544aaca81152d6f2ea790","tid":1834314,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T10:59:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5dbc4933583129b4547db59959ac8ff16149ad12","tid":1834314,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:01:15.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"2bd55c35422532fb316ebb805489577178ac379e","tid":1834314,"uid":37303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:02:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3bae073aa45ea7ca4faf836887e00363f3923955","tid":1834314,"uid":252620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-22T11:02:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b91c5647e2b14b5e429cd074b18cf